Package: dropbear-ssh-service
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Tom Dewey <tom.dewey@raspberrypi.com>
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Description: Lightweight SSH server using dropbear
 Generates host keys on first boot and runs dropbear in the foreground
 as a systemd service. Requires an authorized_keys file to be
 pre-populated in the image for access.
